azure-cli - Azure CLI Wrapper

USAGE:
    azure-cli [azure-cli-arguments...]

DESCRIPTION:
    Azure CLI wrapper that activates Python virtual environment
    before running Azure CLI commands.

ARGUMENTS:
    azure-cli-arguments
        Any valid Azure CLI arguments

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-azure-venv PATH
        Path to Azure CLI Python virtual environment

EXAMPLES:
    azure-cli login
    azure-cli group list
    azure-cli vm create --resource-group myRG --name myVM
